Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.68,0:00:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad was invited to a party on short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.89,0:00:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why Uncle took out his special occasion outfit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:13.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.15,0:00:14.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.90,0:00:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:22.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was thinking maybe I should get a nicer tie for Shin'ichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.62,0:00:33.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you turn all red, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:35.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:37.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And where's Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the barber's.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:40.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's pretty late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.67,0:00:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I-I'll go get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.80,0:00:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flowers dance to the piano's rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:00:51.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two people face-to-face is a mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:53.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not seeing anything despite being at the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:00:54.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is this perplexed eye-witness?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:57.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:00:59.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:56.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do those shops have to be full, especially today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're already closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:21.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So another customer is ahead of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:25.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, do mine first and I'll come to your shop from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:26.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:29.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's deeply relaxing, so I'll do yours first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:31.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:35.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're they gonna serve at the party tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:45.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would be nice if it were French cuisine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:51.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chinese food is good too —\hshark fin and Peking duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like the shuttle bus of the newly opened swimming school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:02.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noisy as always, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:05.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So noisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want me to sue you for noise violation!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:09.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cut it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just hurry and go somewhere else, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:17.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noisy, noisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:22.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:28.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:39.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ebihara!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:47.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You weren't at your usual shop so it took a while to find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:49.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Did you see anyone suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:52.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't, but is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call the police now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:04:58.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:00.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't come inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:05.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:11.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, let's fly it one more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Genta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.57,0:05:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did anyone come out from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:19.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:20.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:25.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:30.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:33.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A murder right behind my back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:34.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How dare they!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, you are —\h?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the famous detective, Mouri Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the famous...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan, is it a case again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:50.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, no kids allowed here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:53.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That includes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:54.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it does...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:06:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, as I turned my head after getting startled by the noise,\NI saw the shop owner Ebihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} lying on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:05.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had already stopped breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.54,0:06:11.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so you heard everything as the crime was taking place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What you heard was the sound of these dropping on the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:17.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:24.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were on the cashier counter, so I suspect Ebihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nknocked those over with his elbow as he was falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That single dart... why is it lying way over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:34.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you were in a deep sleep at the time Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} entered this shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:40.47,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:44.84,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}Noda Masao (43)\NClock Shop Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:44.84,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That's why I didn't notice Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What time did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:53.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had been looking for barber shops that were\Nvacant, so I didn't take note of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the incident happened only a few minutes after I got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:03.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The 1-1-0 call was placed at 6:36 PM, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s arrival would be approximately 6:30 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:11.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what time did you arrive here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:14.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around 6:20 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:20.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I was just overly tired, but as soon as\NI got on the chair, I fell into a deep sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:27.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, during the incident, no one else was\Nentering or exiting the shop, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.75,0:07:33.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, the shuttle bus from the\Nswimming school was in front of the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think it was possible to enter or exit without being seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't see anyone coming out of the shop, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And no one left through the back door either?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:46.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope, not a single person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:49.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were playing in the vacant lot behind the shop the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:56.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit may have thrown a dart from\Nthe outside and killed Ebihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:03.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The swimming school shuttle bus was\Nincidentally playing loud music at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet he opened the window in order to complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.41,0:08:12.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're saying the culprit anticipated that,\Nand threw a dart at him from the outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit was probably hiding in the\Nalley on the opposite side of the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:23.52,Signs,,0,0,0,,Culprit
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:23.52,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ebihara
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:23.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's about 4 meters from the alley to this shop —\Nnot a far-fetched distance for a dart to travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tip of the dart was dabbed with poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, why did Ebihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wear a wig?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,True, it doesn't seem like he needed one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know why, Noda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:38.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:43.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His reason for wearing a wig...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:48.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ebihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is wearing an uncommon sweatshirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the sweatshirt from the Darts Hearts Club,\Nformed by the regulars at a nearby dart bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:57.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Darts Hearts...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:08:58.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:04.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A regular at a darts bar was killed by a dart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This could mean that the culprit is a regular at that darts bar, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These two frequent that darts bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:20.12,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Shimazaki Nozomu (28)\NLinen Services Employee
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:20.60,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,An employee from a linen service company,\NShimazaki Nozomu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:26.50,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,A pharmacist who works at a nearby\Ndrugstore, Koike Tatsutarou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:26.50,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}Koike Tatsutarou (45)\NPharmacist
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm told that you two were arguing with\NEbihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} at the darts bar last night, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:38.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because that old man Ebihara was blabbering\Nthings that were neither here nor there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Neither here nor there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:46.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Shima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} has been embezzling from\Nthe company," was what Ebi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, Shima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} flew into a rage and grabbed\Nhim by his chest, so I went to stop them was all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:54.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cut the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:10:01.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he said you've been selling drugs on the black market in an\Nattempt to overcome your debt, your face turned blue, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:07.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, Noda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:09.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't recovered from your cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:11.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's your mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I seem to have dropped it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you, Noda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may stand there pretending everything's cool, but\Nyou've been borrowing from old man Ebihara, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, Ebi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} said that he's been footing\Nthe bill for your store's operating costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.34,0:10:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did borrow from him, but it wasn't a large amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the incident took place, Noda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, weren't you at the shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:37.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that most suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:43.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, during Ebihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s murder, Noda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nwas sitting on the chair next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be impossible for him to commit the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you supposed to be, with such a big attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:51.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the famous detective Mouri Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sleeping Kogoro!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, at approximately 6:30 PM...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:10:59.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where were you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:02.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You first, Koike{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:04.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in my drugstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.21,0:11:07.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can someone else confirm your statement?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:08.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:13.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No customers came, and my wife was in the kitchen preparing dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:16.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So no one else?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:17.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:19.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shimazaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:25.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around 6:30 PM, I think I was still in the middle of a delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:27.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, I did stop by a gasoline station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gasoline station?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, if I were to contact the manager, would\Nthey be able to confirm your whereabouts?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I used a self-serve pump, so I\Ndidn't come across the manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I have the receipt here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,6:24 PM...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:48.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From that gas station to this shop, it would\Ntake at least thirty minutes even by car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:51.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi did see that person earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:53.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In front of this shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:58.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was coming out the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:12:00.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About what time did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:02.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sometime in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:06.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, I could see the clock inside this shop through the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was 5:50!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:13.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,4:15!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:15.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,7:45?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:23.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That clock has its left and right reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:25.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's for customers to see in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:26.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you finally got one of those?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:31.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a regular clock before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, when did you get one in stock?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:35.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:42.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, the time Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} saw\NShimazaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wasn't at 5:50, but 6:10.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:50.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you came out of here at 6:10, it would be impossible\Nfor you to have arrived at the gas station at 6:24.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I did come here to pick up the towels!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:13:01.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although we had a fight about things that happened last\Nnight, I left quickly because I had other deliveries to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was as she said —\hbefore six o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:10.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we told you, that clock has its display\Nflipped horizontally, so it was 6:10.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wrong, it was before six o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shimazaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:18.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your embezzling was discovered by Ebihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, so you killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nonsense...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you left the shop, you hid in the alley,\Nwaiting for Ebihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to open the windows...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:28.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't make that with my skills...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:31.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the worst rookie in Darts Hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, Koike{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:35.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:40.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the most skilled among our group!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.16,0:13:42.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tip of the dart used in the murder was laced with poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:47.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a pharmacist, Koike{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} could've easily concocted a poison, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:50.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:53.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Koike{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}... The culprit is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:55.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:57.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So who is the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:14:01.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a famous detective, he should really be more specific on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He seems unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.06,0:14:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,YOU BRATS, SCRAM!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:10.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsk, stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:14.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We even gave them important witness statements!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:15.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If a poisoned dart was prepared, then this was a premeditated crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's so, would they really throw it from this far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't see the clock through the windows!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, you said you saw the clock, but from where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.35,0:14:46.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.02,0:14:46.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:49.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How weird, I can't see the clock now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I really saw it earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The clock was moved?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:55.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:04.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit is that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shimazaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Koike{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please come\Nto the station for further questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:30.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:37.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will reveal the truth at this very moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:43.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:47.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you figured out who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually the culprit was already in the shop before I arrived...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he's still among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:57.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, the culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.76,0:16:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:03.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During that entire time, I was sitting right next to you, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you heard something fall on the floor and looked back...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:24.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said Noda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} also got up from the chair next to you, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ebihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wasn't killed at the time the smashing occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:33.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact, he had already been killed before I arrived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:40.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You met with Ebihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} when you got here, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:49.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be exact, a man with an afro who wore a mask,\Nand a blue sweatshirt saying "Darts Hearts" on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:51.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that was Ebihara!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:55.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wrong, that was you in disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Disguise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:17:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of my sudden visit, you quickly put on\Na wig and a mask to hide your face from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:06.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you actually still have your mask, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, where was Ebihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:12.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was in the chair next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Covered with an apron and a hot towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you killed Ebihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} at this shop, you were\Nplanning to leave by pretending nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:30.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I came in instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:35.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In a rush, you put on a disguise and introduced yourself as the owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:42.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, you put a hot towel on me to cover my\Neyes, and tried to escape through the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, there were kids in the backyard, and you couldn't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were people in front of the shop too,\Nso you were cornered inside like a mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that very moment, the swimming school's shuttle bus came.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuttle bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:18:03.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While the bus was playing that noisy and\Nloud music, you came up with an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using that music to your advantage, you would\Nswitch yourself with the body on the chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:10.10,Signs,,0,0,0,,And managed to become the primary discoverer along with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Under that loud volume, small sounds would go unnoticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You quickly laid the body in front of the\Ncounter, and got in the chair yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, how did he make everything fall from the counter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He threw a dart at those —\hthe single dart\Nlying on the floor near the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:32.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:35.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, he pretended to be awakened by the smashing noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But tell me, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:48.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did Noda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} have to put the body in the chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:50.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't think you'd come, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:55.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ebihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was killed while he was sitting on the chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would a barber shop owner sit in his own chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was checking the position of the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The position of the clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:08.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That clock was brought here before the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.99,0:19:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I looked from the outside just a while ago, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, where did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't see the clock through the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You couldn't see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:22.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The clock was hanging right over there, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:27.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:29.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was over there before!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:32.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's over there, we could see it from the outside, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:38.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} witnessed Shimazaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s presence,\Nthe clock was still hanging in the old position.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:44.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, Noda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} came and\Nreplaced the clock with a flipped one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:49.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, in order to check the angle, Ebihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} sat on the chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then restrained him from behind and stabbed him with the dart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, you put a towel over his\Nface and covered him with an apron.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:01.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, even if people peeked in from the outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.79,0:20:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They would think a customer was waiting for a shave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, you arrived before he could escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:12.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wait, where's the original clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's in the shoecase near the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:16.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:22.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said about meeting me\Nin disguise earlier, do you have proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:23.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:29.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Under your T-shirt is the sweatshirt from the Darts Hearts club, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.07,0:20:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.45,0:20:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No logo or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:57.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't seriously think I'd be fooled\Nby such a childish trick, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:00.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi, relieve Noda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} of his shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.81,0:21:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:05.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, allow me to do my job...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:05.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:07.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:19.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you wore it backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He hastily changed it while switching himself with the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.25,0:21:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one other than the culprit has any reason to wear it backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:30.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:38.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The IOU Ebihara forced me to write\Nwhen I borrowed money from him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was transfered to the loan sharks without me knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:47.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been receiving threats everyday,\Nand my wife developed neurosis...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did Ebihara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:54.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was the one who borrowed money from the loan sharks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.53,0:21:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to write off his debt, he sold me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:21:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could he...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't forgive...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.79,0:22:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That terrible guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.63,0:23:32.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.92,0:23:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to be treated tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.84,0:23:40.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After he solved the case, he kept sleeping all the way through?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.97,0:23:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, soundly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.31,0:23:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he didn't make it to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.27,0:23:53.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, another cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.65,0:23:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry that you couldn't enjoy fancy cuisine, Uncle...
